01:10:29,760 --> 01:10:31,060
Sbohem.

826
01:10:35,620 --> 01:10:37,920
Je to náš šťastný konec?

827
01:10:39,160 --> 01:10:40,190
To je...

828
01:10:40,920 --> 01:10:42,820
instinkt té chvíle...

829
01:10:43,590 --> 01:10:44,920
a kompletní...

830
01:10:45,420 --> 01:10:47,660
začátek lidské volby.

831
01:10:51,420 --> 01:10:52,690
Omlouvám se.

832
01:10:54,990 --> 01:10:56,890
Je mi to líto.